column2: SELECT TOP #  s.apogee_id,s.ra, s.dec, s.glon, s.glat,  s.vhelio_avg,s.vscatter,  a.teff, a.teff_err, a.logg, a.logg_err, a.param_m_h, a.param_m_h_err,  a.param_alpha_m, a.param_alpha_m_err,  dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlagN(a.aspxcapflag),  dbo.fApogeeStarFlagN(s.starflag) FROM apogeeStar s  JOIN aspcapStar a on a.apstar_id = s.apstar_id WHERE (a.aspxcapflag & dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlag(&&&)) = # and  s.commiss = # and  (s.apogee_target1 &  (dbo.fApogeeTarget1(&&&)+  dbo.fApogeeTarget1(&&&)+  dbo.fApogeeTarget1(&&&))) != #
